deals.title: Chicken Noodle Soup (Pho Ga)
deals.itemDescription: Smooth rice noodles in chicken broth topped with chicken. Served with a side of vegetables, bean sprouts, and onions. Pho noodle soup (pho) is a famous traditional dish and specialty of Vietnam. It is made from smooth rice noodles, tender beef or chicken, and the flavors broth which has been steamed for hours. Pho is not only delicious but also carries the essence of Vietnamese culinary culture.
